ndshake request received from node terminal.`,\n172 |         `[IDENTITY] Resolved profile context: ${mockUser.role.toUpperCase()}`,\n173 |         `[SSL/TLS] Session handshake initiated via SHA-256 cipher.`,\n174 |         `[SECURITY] Clearance key resolved: ${mockUser.clearance.split(\" \")[2] || \"L-3\"}-${generatedHash}`,\n175 |         `[SANDBOX] Memory enclave isolated. Sandbox state: READY.`\n176 |       ];\n177 |       setTelemetryLogs(logs);\n178 |     }\n179 |   }, [selectedRole]);\n180 | \n181 |   const handleInputChange = (field: string, val: string) => {\n182 |     if (field === \"email\") {\n183 |       setEmail(val);\n184 |       if (val.length % 3 === 0) {\n185 |         logTelemetry(`[INPUT] Term buffer parsed: ${val.substring(0, 15)}${val.length > 15 ? \"...\" : \"\"} (resolving DNS)`);\n186 |       }\n187 |     } else if (field === \"password\") {\n188 |       setPassword(val);\n189 |       if (val.length % 2 === 0) {\n190 |         const hashPart = getDeterministicHash(val, 4);\n191 |         logTelemetry(`[CRYPT] Salted passphrase vector: SHA-512_SALT_${hashPart}`);\n192 |       }\n193 |     } else if (field === \"otp\") {\n194 |       setOtpCode(val);\n195 |       if (val.length === 6) {\n196 |         logTelemetry(`[OTP] Multi-factor authentication block complete. Ready for clearance verification.`);\n197 |       }\n198 |     }\n199 |   };\n200 | \n201 |   const logTelemetry = (msg: string) => {\n202 |     setTelemetryLogs(prev => [...prev.slice(-12), msg]);\n203 |   };\n204 | \n205 |   useEffect(() => {\n206 |     if (consoleBottomRef.current) {\n207 |       consoleBottomRef.current.scrollIntoView({ behavior: \"smooth\" });\n208 |     }\n209 |   }, [telemetryLogs]);\n210 | \n211 |   const handleAuthenticate = async () => {\n212 |     setScanning(true);\n213 |     setScanStep(0);\n214 |     \n215 |     const stepIntervals = [250, 300, 350, 400];\n216 |     for (let i = 0; i < stepIntervals.length; i++) {\n217 |       await new Promise(r => set